  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Stroke patients

          -  Subject with gripping ability: capable of peeling off the connected object from the
             table, presented in its grip area.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe cognitive disorders preventing the completion of the task

          -  Bilateral brain lesions
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
